translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_fe19211a:

    # n "Wait, what do you mean..."
    n "Espera, ¿de qué hablas...?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:183
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_ec1eb267:

    # ks smile "You remember, Nozomi. How appropriate it is to feel so drowsy, so sleepy, as the light passes your eyes."
    ks smile "Recuerda, Nozomi. Cuán apropiado es sentirte tan adormecida, tan soñolienta, mientras la luz pasa por tus ojos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:185
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_f0261495:

    # ks "Your eyelids becoming heavier, with every pass of the light."
    ks "Tus párpados se ponen pesados, con cada pasar de la luz."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:222
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_d8a1cb1e:

    # ks "Eyelids getting heavier. Impossible to keep them open."
    ks "Tus párpados pesan. Es imposible mantenerlos abiertos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:190
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_168ab416:

    # ks "Sleep, Nozomi."
    ks "Duerme, Nozomi."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:228
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_45679d07:

    # n sleep "..."
    n sleep "..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:192
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_7cc363ee:

    # "Wonderful. That was faster than before, but we have next to no time left if we want to get back to class without raising any suspicions."
    "Maravilloso. Fue más rápido que antes, pero tenemos poco tiempo si queremos regresar a clase sin levantar sospechas."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:193
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_55246854:

    # "But it should be enough time to remind Nozomi just how good a thing we have going here."
    "Aunque debería ser suficiente para recordarle a Nozomi lo grandioso que es lo que estamos haciendo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:194
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_1fa56f89:

    # ks "Now Nozomi, I want you to recall how much you enjoy meeting with me like this. How right it feels."
    ks "Ahora, Nozomi, quiero que recuerdes lo mucho que disfrutas el reunirte conmigo. Lo bien que se siente."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:195
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_d711e589:

    # ks "Focus on that feeling, Nozomi; your desire to meet with me. Let it grow in your mind, feeling more right, more natural, to want to spend time with me."
    ks "Concéntrate en ese sentimiento, Nozomi; tu deseo de volver a verme. Que crezca en tu mente, y que se sienta más correcto, más natural querer pasar tiempo conmigo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:196
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_8d8df7ad:

    # ks "With that in mind, Nozomi, it's only natural and right that you will want to act on this desire of yours. Don't you agree?"
    ks "Con eso en mente, Nozomi, es natural y correcto que quieras reaccionar a ese deseo. ¿No estás de acuerdo?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:197
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_8aa8dd2d:

    # n sleeptalk "Agree..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "De acuerdo..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:199
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_156f35d0:

    # ks "That's right. Only natural and right that you act on your desire to meet with me again." with dissolve
    ks "Eso es. Es natural y correcto que reacciones a ese deseo de volver a verme." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:200
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_cb94d4bf:

    # "She seems to be taking to this well, but I can't help but feel frustrated by these short sessions."
    "Parece estarse tomándolo bien, pero no puedo evitar sentirme frustrado con una sesión tan corta."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:201
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_b009827f:

    # "I hope soon we'll be able to spend some real time together, and perhaps now she herself will help me with that."
    "Espero que pronto podamos pasar tiempo juntos de verdad, y quizá ahora ella misma me ayude con eso."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:202
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_845b3ad9:

    # ks "Keep this desire of yours at the back of your mind and forget the fact that you were hypnotized."
    ks "Guarda ese deseo en lo profundo de tu mente y olvida el hecho de que fuiste hipnotizada."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:203
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_b0618146:

    # ks "Now slowly begin to awaken as I count to five."
    ks "Ahora despierta lentamente mientras cuento hasta cinco."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:205
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_c3d4b0f3:

    # ks "One... two... forgetting that you were hypnotized."
    ks "Uno... dos... olvidando que fuiste hipnotizada."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:206
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_a2461a70:

    # ks "Three... four... more awake. Opening your eyes."
    ks "Tres... cuatro... cada vez más despierta. Abre tus ojitos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:208
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_fec60368:

    # ks "Five." with dissolve
    ks "Cinco." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:209
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_cbdd7891:

    # n neutral "Hm?" with dissolve
    n neutral "¿Mm?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:210
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_581df466:

    # ks smile "I was just saying, thanks for sticking up for me earlier. It meant a lot to me."
    ks smile "Te decía que gracias por dar la cara por mí hace rato. Significó mucho para mí."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:211
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_5aed8439:

    # n smile "Oh... of course, Kyou. Anytime~" with dissolve
    n smile "Oh... por supuesto, Kyou. Cuando quieras." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:212
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_03073c65:

    # ks "Now we'd better hurry back to class."
    ks "Ahora, démonos prisa, hay que ir a clase."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:217
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_57d53472:

    # "As I say that the school bell sounds, prompting us to dash back to class without further delay."
    "En cuanto digo eso, suena la campana de la escuela y corremos sin demora de regreso al aula."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:220
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_9e0a0913:

    # "The rest of the day passed without incident."
    "El resto del día transcurrió sin incidentes."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:221
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_ee51cc13:

    # "I had hoped to spend some more time with Nozomi after school but her club activities kept her away."
    "Esperaba pasar más tiempo con Nozomi después de la escuela, pero sus actividades de club la mantuvieron lejos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:222
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_e77c81b1:

    # "I know I need to be patient. As far as I can tell our hypnosis sessions have already had a profound effect on her, so it surely won't be long before we meet up again."
    "Sé que debo ser paciente. Hasta donde sé, nuestras sesiones de hipnosis tuvieron un profundo efecto sobre ella, por lo que no pasará mucho antes de que nos volvamos a ver."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:223
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_8b199800:

    # "To think after all this time she accepts me and wants to see more of me, and all it took was a little push at the back of her mind."
    "Y pensar que, después de todo este tiempo, por fin me acepta y quiere ver más de mí, y solo hizo falta un empujoncito a lo que guardaba su mente."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:261
translate spanish Day2_NonCon_Kyou_d2e1bf39:

    # "I knew it. I KNEW she was interested in me!"
    "Lo sabía. ¡SABÍA que estaba interesada en mí!"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:231
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_9471698f:

    # "If yesterday's classes were boring, today's are just torture."
    "Si las clases de ayer fueron aburridas, las de hoy son una tortura."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:232
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_20663a05:

    # "I'm managing to focus on the subject matter through sheer force of will, although I still can't stop thinking of Nozomi entirely."
    "Logro concentrarme en el tema en cuestión por mera fuerza de voluntad, aunque los pensamientos sobre Nozomi no se van del todo de mi cabeza."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:233
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_db6fa7c2:

    # "Like, what is she thinking now that she's had time to consider what happened?"
    "¿Qué estará pensando ahora que tuvo tiempo de reflexionar sobre lo que ocurrió?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:234
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_dbc32c9b:

    # "Is she perhaps coming round to the idea that we could be together?"
    "¿Estará considerando la idea de que podamos estar juntos?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:254
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_e07b83eb:

    # "She averts her eyes as she catches me looking at her. She seemed a little anxious." with dissolve
    "Aparta la mirada después de atraparme viendo hacia ella. Parece un tanto ansiosa." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:241
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_9c71354b:

    # "I guess it's to be expected. She's scared to admit how she feels deep down, and that's just going to make talking to her again more difficult."
    "Supongo que es de esperarse. Le asusta admitir lo que siente en el fondo, y eso solo hará que volver a hablar con ella sea más difícil."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:242
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_af5ee6df:

    # "What to do..."
    "¿Qué debo hacer?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:259
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_663b6c19:

    # "Eventually the lunch bell rings and I'm immediately looking across to find out what Nozomi is doing once more."
    "Eventualmente suena la campana del almuerzo y una vez más miro desde mi escritorio para ver qué está haciendo Nozomi."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:252
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_5ed905fa:

    # h "Nozo! What's up?"
    h "¡Nozo! ¿Qué te pasa?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:254
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_5de48e40:

    # n "Hm? What... what do you mean?" with dissolve
    n "¿Mm? ¿A... a qué te refieres?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:256
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_69771bc3:

    # h sad_side "I mean you've been tense as shit all morning. Something wrong?" with dissolve
    h sad_side "Me refiero a que has estado tensa como la mierda toda la mañana. ¿Ocurre algo?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:267
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_41b4c212:

    # n "It's... Well, I don't know what to tell you, honestly." with dissolve
    n "Es que... Pues, honestamente no sé qué decirte." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:258
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_d77d259c:

    # s concerned "That does seem concerning. Is there anything we can do?" with dissolve
    s concerned "Suena preocupante. ¿Hay algo que podamos hacer?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:270
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_b21f095e:

    # n sad "I'm not sure..."
    n sad "No estoy segura..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:260
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_047be92a:

    # "She catches my gaze on her from across the room again, before quickly breaking contact as she returns her attention to those friends of hers."
    "Me atrapa mirándola desde la otra esquina del aula, para luego romper rápidamente el contacto y volver su atención a esas dos amigas suyas."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:261
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_0c4294d5:

    # n sad_closed "We'll talk on the roof." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Hablaremos en la azotea." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:277
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_a39097fd:

    # "And with that she walks out of the classroom, the other two filing out behind her."
    "Y dicho eso sale del salón con las otras dos caminando detrás de ella."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:266
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_cdbdc07c:

    # "I have to follow them."
    "Tengo que seguirlas."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:283
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_01c6eda5:

    # "As I arrive at the rooftop, I can see the three of them have already sat themselves down by the roof's edge."
    "En cuanto llego a la azotea, puedo ver que las tres ya se han sentado junto al borde del techo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:313
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_31c22ce1:

    # "I don't know what Nozomi has been saying in the time I wasn't able to overhear, but both her friends seem to scowl at me as they see me arrive."
    "No sé qué estuvo diciendo Nozomi mientras no pude escuchar a escondidas, pero sus amigas me fruncen ambas el ceño en cuanto me ven llegar."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:287
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_21668ae0:

    # "... Maybe I'd better keep my distance for now. The pair of them look like they'd throw me off the roof if I got near them."
    "... Tal vez sea mejor que mantenga mi distancia por ahora. El par luce como si pensara tirarme del techo si me acerco."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:316
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_e1bf5d76:

    # "They can't keep me from having lunch up here though, so I guess I'll hang around and enjoy the view. By myself."
    "Aunque no pueden evitar que almuerce aquí. Supongo que pasaré el tiempo y disfrutaré la vista. Yo solo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:292
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_557170a7:

    # "As usual..."
    "Como siempre..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:293
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_3b0624af:

    # "But damn, it's driving me nuts."
    "Pero, demonios, esto me está volviendo loco."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:294
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_eebfeb72:

    # "What is she saying to them? Is she really telling them how I hypnotized her yesterday?"
    "¿Qué les estará diciendo? ¿Les estará contando cómo la hipnoticé ayer?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:295
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_13f81ee1:

    # "The only reason she fell into a trance yesterday is because deep down, she WANTED to be hypnotized. It wouldn't have worked otherwise."
    "La única razón por la que cayó en trance fue porque, en el fondo, ella QUERÍA ser hipnotizada. De lo contrario, no habría funcionado."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:298
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_219fb6fe:

    # "Ditto with the conversation I had with her while she was under."
    "Lo mismo con la conversación que tuve con ella durante el trance."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:299
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_6d225b72:

    # "If she truly disagreed with what I was saying, she would've said so, or she would've woken up from hypnosis if she was really that weirded out by it."
    "De haber estado en desacuerdo con lo que decía, lo habría dicho, o habría despertado de la hipnosis si en serio la hubiera incomodado."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:300
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_1296c4d4:

    # "There was no way I could've forced her to change her mind about me."
    "No pude haberla obligado a cambiar lo que piensa de mí."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:301
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_b24f92de:

    # "So why is she even this freaked out? Is she just embarrassed to admit to herself that she was considering giving me a chance?"
    "Entonces, ¿por qué está tan asustada? ¿Acaso le avergüenza admitirse a sí misma que estaba considerando darme una oportunidad?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:340
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_26b6e2a5:

    # "Is this her way of dealing with the shame?"
    "¿Es así como lidia con la pena?"

# TODO: Translation updated at 2024-07-01 10:47

# game/kyou 2.rpy:303
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_65aad996:

    # "The shame of wanting to be hypnotized by Kyou Koyama, class creep, if you believe some of the rumours."
    "La pena de querer ser hipnotizada por Kyou Koyama, el bicho raro de la clase, si es que crees los rumores."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:304
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_78e63c68:

    # "It makes me mad thinking about it."
    "Me enfurece pensar en eso."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:316
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_b8ffed67:

    # "As lunch comes to an end the three of them walk past me to get to the exit." with dissolve
    "El almuerzo llega a su fin y las tres me evitan al caminar hacia la salida." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:317
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_2d45f21f:

    # "They don't say anything, but the looks Nozomi's friends are giving me are suggesting I'd better watch myself."
    "No dicen nada, pero las miradas que me muestran las amigas de Nozomi me sugieren que mejor tenga cuidado."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:318
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_f160f384:

    # "I know a little about those two girls..."
    "No sé mucho de esas dos chicas..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:319
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_07fe9c5c:

    # "The angry little brattish woman is Hiroko, from the tennis club. She likes to pick on me whenever I accidentally wind up in her orbit."
    "La pequeña mocosa enojona es Hiroko, del club de tenis. Le gusta molestarme cada vez que accidentalmente me cruzo en su órbita."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:320
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_256af55d:

    # "The taller one is Sayori, who barely looks like she can stay awake in class half the time. She'd be as anonymous as me if it weren't for the company she keeps."
    "La alta es Sayori, quien la mitad del tiempo parece que apenas puede mantenerse despierta en clase. Sería tan invisible como yo de no ser por la compañía que tiene."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:321
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_336c0cb2:

    # "As it is, none of the girls in this school will give me the time of day."
    "Ninguna chica en esta escuela me muestra el mínimo respeto."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:322
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_3d90ca77:

    # "Once those two go off some more about my latest \"creepy\" behaviour I'm sure everyone's going to be even shittier to me."
    "En cuanto esas dos abran la boca sobre mi \"espeluznante\" comportamiento, todos me tratarán todavía más como mierda."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:323
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_f49a57e7:

    # "It's really fucking unfair, but that's what I've come to expect from people now."
    "Qué puta injusticia, pero ¿qué más puedo esperar ahora de la gente?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:326
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_f9f3d4b4:

    # "After lunch, the rest of the school day passed uneventfully."
    "Después del almuerzo, el resto de las clases transcurren sin más acontecimientos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:374
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_47d77681:

    # "I watch as Nozomi exits the classroom with a haste that I have to admit is pretty unusual for her."
    "Veo a Nozomi salir del salón con una prisa que, he de admitir, es muy inusual de su parte."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:334
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_b870f046:

    # "As I leave behind her, I notice her walking briskly towards the classrooms typically used for club activities." with dissolve
    "Salgo detrás de ella y la noto caminando enérgicamente hacia las aulas que suelen usarse para los clubs." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:335
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_50dca984:

    # "She heads the literature club, and I know this is a meeting day."
    "Se dirige al club de literatura y sé que hoy es día de reunión."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:337
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_8f0012fe:

    # "I don't have a club of my own to go to, but maybe I could hang around and wait for her to come out?"
    "Yo no tengo un club al que ir, ¿pero tal vez pueda quedarme por aquí y esperar a que salga?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:343
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_f279049a:

    # "I think about waiting, but she'll be in there for hours and loitering around school is just going to get me in trouble."
    "Pienso en esperar, pero estará ahí por horas y merodear por la escuela solo me meterá en problemas."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:344
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_8347b431:

    # "With a sigh, I start to head home."
    "Con un suspiro, me voy camino a casa."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:345
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_8738aabe:

    # "Maybe tomorrow she'll be in a better frame of mind to talk to me."
    "Tal vez mañana esté en un mejor estado de ánimo para hablar conmigo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:348
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_4bcecb1d:

    # "I'll stop by the convenience store on the way. Pick up some comfort treats to soothe the pain of longing in my gut."
    "Pasaré por la tienda de conveniencia de camino. Compraré algunas golosinas para aliviar el dolor que siento en las entrañas."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:350
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_2cb10cb0:

    # h "Hey, asshole!" with dissolve
    h "¡Oye, pendejo!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:351
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_d4274aab:

    # ks surprised "H-huh?!"
    ks surprised "¡¿E-eh?!"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:352
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_05a36c39:

    # "Oh, it's Hiroko. Nozomi's obnoxious mouthy friend from the tennis club."
    "Oh, es Hiroko. La odiosa amiga bocona de Nozomi del club de tenis."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:353
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_bfd11f58:

    # "She's always had a problem with me for some reason, from the very first day we met. But for her to follow me into town?"
    "Por alguna razón, siempre ha tenido un problema conmigo, desde el día en que la conocí. ¿Pero en serio me siguió hasta acá?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:355
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_2a2f96e7:

    # h angry "I dunno what your deal is, but you better back the fuck off of Nozomi or you're gonna need a new {nw}" with dissolve
    h angry "No sé qué es lo que tramas, pero será mejor que mantengas tu culo alejado de Nozomi ¡o necesitarás una {nw}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:356
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_8db86b8c:

    # extend "FACE by the time I'm done with you!" with vpunch
    extend "CARA NUEVA cuando termine contigo!" with vpunch

# game/kyou 2.rpy:357
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_742b0a0b:

    # "This isn't even the first time this little shit has threatened me."
    "Ni siquiera es la primera vez que este trozo de mierda me amenaza."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:358
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_380743c8:

    # "To think that I can be pushed around by a female classmate, and one a full head shorter than me at that."
    "Y pensar que una chica de mi clase me puede mangonear, y una más baja que yo por una cabeza, por cierto."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:360
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_d7a4d64d:

    # ks annoyed "What... What are you even saying? Why do you care if I'm around her or not?"
    ks annoyed "¿Qué... qué estás diciendo? ¿A ti qué te importa si estoy cerca de ella o no?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:361
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_233152e1:

    # h uniform_armup "You freaked her out big time, you fuckin' creepo. {w=0.8}{nw}" with dissolve
    h uniform_armup "La asustase, bicho raro de mierda. {w=0.8}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:362
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_3ded802c:

    # extend "DON'T go near her!" with vpunch
    extend "¡NO te acerques a ella!" with vpunch

# game/kyou 2.rpy:363
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_09cf11c2:

    # "Goddamn, is this what it's going to be like from now on? Constant harassment?"
    "Maldita sea. ¿Así serán las cosas a partir de ahora? ¿Acoso constante?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:364
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_c8e5bd0c:

    # "Onlookers are starting to appear because she's more or less screaming at me and it's making me tense as fuck."
    "Ya hay algunos mirones porque básicamente me está gritando y eso me pone de los putos nervios."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:365
