    # ks smile "That's right, Hiroko. You're a [hypno6!t] with a CPU that processes data and instructions." with dissolve
    ks smile "Así es, Hiroko. Eres un[genero_a] [hypno6!t] con una CPU que procesa datos e instrucciones." with dissolve

