translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_9c55742b:

    # ks "That's right, Hiroko. It feels good for you to say it aloud, to accept the truth of what you are." with dissolve
    ks "Así es, Hiroko. Se siente bien decirlo en voz alta, aceptar la verdad de lo que eres." with dissolve

