translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_4baf0b8c:

    # ks "And as I said, I have hacked into your programming and altered it. That's why you are now aware that you're a [hypno6]."
    ks "Y como dije, he hackeado tu programación y la he alterado. Es por eso que ahora estás consciente de que eres un[genero_a] [hypno6!t]."

