    # ks "That means going straight back to this exact state you are in now. Blank. Open-eyed. Completely relaxed and deeply in trance."
    ks "Eso quiere decir que regresará exactamente a este estado. En blanco. Ojos abiertos. Completamente relajada y en un profundo trance."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1016
