    # ncg "O-of course... And this is my first time doing hypnosis one-to-one."
    ncg "P-por supuesto... Y esta es mi primera vez haciendo hipnosis uno a uno."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1763
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_750d4330:

    # ncg "It's a different feeling to when I was with Satoshi and the others."
    ncg "Se siente diferente a cuando estaba con Satoshi y los demás."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1764
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_934edf64:

    # "I smile back at her as my mind races."
    "Le devuelvo la sonrisa y mi mente se acelera."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1765
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_db55dd69:

    # "I'm so fucking excited, but I gotta stay calm, concentrate, and show her what I've learned."
    "Carajo, estoy tan emocionado, pero debo guardar la calma, concentrarme, y mostrarle lo que he aprendido."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1766
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_426bd295:

    # ks smile "So, I... I guess we should talk about what we want to happen here?"
    ks smile "Pues, supongo... ¿supongo que deberíamos hablar de lo que queremos que ocurra?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1768
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_734dd472:

    # ncg stern "Oh yes, right." with dissolve
    ncg stern "Oh, sí, cierto." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1769
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0a70c117:

    # ks "We should keep it nice and simple to start."
    ks "Deberíamos mantenerlo simple para empezar."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1770
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8340e553:

    # ncg "Of course. So I was thinking, we try putting me into a trance and then keeping me there a few minutes before slowly taking me back out?"
    ncg "Por supuesto. Estaba pensando: ¿intentamos ponerme en trance y luego mantenerme ahí unos cuantos minutos antes sacarme lentamente?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1771
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_92a3860b:

    # "It might be my excitement spilling out, but I can't help but chuckle at her suggestion."
    "Podrá ser la emoción desbordándose, pero no puedo evitar reírme un poco de su sugerencia."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1772
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_89c1831e:

    # ncg neutral "What's so funny?" with dissolve
    ncg neutral "¿Qué es tan gracioso?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1773
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_70db7a75:

    # ks "I don't know. That seems a little TOO simple."
    ks "No lo sé. Eso parece DEMASIADO simple."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2382
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_12c92e2a:

    # ncg uniform folded annoyed "W-well, someone feels sure of himself. Don't you think trancing me is challenge enough for a first time?" with dissolve
    ncg uniform folded annoyed "V-vaya, alguien se siente muy confiado. ¿No crees que ponerme en trance es reto suficiente para la primera vez?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1775
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_544f0f13:

    # ks "Eh, maybe. I just thought we could make it a little more interesting than that."
    ks "Je, tal vez. Solo pensé que podríamos hacerlo un poco más interesante."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1777
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_84cbb77e:

    # "I have a little think about what I could propose. I guess some kind of simple but fun suggestion to prove I can hypnotize her effectively." with dissolve
    "Pienso un poco en qué puedo proponer. Supongo que una sugestión simple pero divertida para probar que puedo hipnotizarla de forma efectiva." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1778
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5917d0bd:

    # "Maybe..."
    "Tal vez..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1782
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_42684f52:

    # ks smile "How about I try to make you forget a number, then have you count to ten?"
    ks smile "¿Qué tal si intentamos hacerte olvidar un número, y luego cuentas hasta diez?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1783
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7a6937b8:

    # ncg neutral "Okay... sure, that's a classic isn't it? You can try that." with dissolve
    ncg neutral "Muy bien... claro, es un clásico, ¿no? Puedes intentar eso." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1786
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f10bb0d9:

    # ks smile "What if I made you think your name was something else?"
    ks smile "¿Qué tal si te hago creer que tu nombre es otro?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1787
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7a6937b8_1:

    # ncg neutral "Okay... sure, that's a classic isn't it? You can try that." with dissolve
    ncg neutral "Muy bien... claro, es un clásico, ¿no? Puedes intentar eso." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1789
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9de041bc:

    # ncg stern "Just... if you somehow manage to pull that off, make sure I don't leave today thinking that." with dissolve
    ncg stern "Pero... si de algún modo logras hacer que funcione, asegúrate de que no me vaya pensando así." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2014
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f5c6a6f3:

    # ncg "I mean, I should go back to thinking normally anyway, but a good hypnotist should always tidy up after themselves. It's a safety thing."
    ncg "Es decir, mis pensamientos deberían regresar a la normalidad de todos modos, pero un buen hipnotista siempre arregla su desorden. Es por seguridad."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1791
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7cb2c06b:

    # ncg stern_closed "Oh, and one other thing, while I'm talking to you about safety." with dissolve
    ncg stern_closed "Oh, y otra cosa, ya que hablamos de seguridad." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1792
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3159a5f8:

    # "Nozomi then dips a hand into her pocket and pulls out her phone? Before unlocking it and handing it to me?"
    "Nozomi sumerge la mano en su bolsillo y... ¿saca su teléfono?... para luego desbloquearlo y... ¿dármelo a mí?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1793
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_cef9cdac:

    # ncg stern "I want you to record this." with dissolve
    ncg stern "Quiero que grabes todo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2425
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dc4b2569:

    # ks confused "What?"
    ks confused "¿Qué?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1795
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_75beb36d:

    # ncg "I'm serious. Set the phone to record video and point it at me. I want to see what happens."
    ncg "Hablo en serio. Presiona el botón de grabar video y apunta el teléfono hacia mí. Quiero ver lo que ocurre."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1796
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8f7a4503:

    # ncg "Plus it's... well, it's for my safety, too."
    ncg "Y además es para... bueno, también es por seguridad."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1797
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c061a403:

    # ks "For your safety?"
    ks "¿Por tu seguridad?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1798
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a0187fbf:

    # ncg stern_closed "Look, I know you shouldn't be able to make people do things they wouldn't normally do under hypnosis, but there are ways around that..." with dissolve
    ncg stern_closed "Mira, sé que se supone que no puedes hacer a la gente hacer cosas que normalmente no haría con hipnosis, pero hay métodos..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1799
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b7b2bace:

    # ncg "And I'm sorry, but I don't fully trust you, Kyou."
    ncg "Y lo siento, pero no confío en ti del todo, Kyou."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1801
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_966976ed:

    # ks sigh "Ouch."
    ks sigh "Auch."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2410
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2a8f141a:

    # ncg standing uniform annoyed "Can you blame me? We've been classmates since our freshman year but I barely know you at all." with dissolve
    ncg standing uniform annoyed "¿Puedes culparme? Hemos sido compañeros de clase desde primer semestre, pero apenas te conozco." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1803
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_78759abf:

    # ncg "And... well, you haven't exactly done your reputation any favours, to be honest."
    ncg "Y... bueno, no has cuidado mucho de tu reputación, para ser honesta."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1804
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5a0c1db3:

    # ks "... Ouch."
    ks "... Auch."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2413
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e393e7f2:

    # ncg standing uniform angry "Oh, suck it up, Kyou. You're getting what you wanted out of this, so don't complain." with dissolve
    ncg standing uniform angry "Ay, por favor, Kyou. Vas a obtener lo que querías de esto, así que no te quejes." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1806
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_1f1c8587:

    # ncg stern "Now, are you recording? Are we ready to start?" with dissolve
    ncg stern "Entonces, ¿estás grabando? ¿Estamos listos para empezar?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1807
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_c9ed8e4f:

    # "Okay, okay, what she said hurts but the last thing I want is a pissed-off Nozomi so I'm not gonna argue. Not when I've come this far."
    "Muy bien, muy bien, lo que dijo duele, pero lo último que quiero es una Nozomi molesta, así que no discutiré. No cuando ya llegué tan lejos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1808
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_70bc0b11:

    # "Instead, I hastily set the recording app to start and point the phone camera at Nozomi as she demands, then dip my hand into my pocket."
    "En efecto, abro apresuradamente la aplicación de grabación y apunto la cámara del teléfono a Nozomi tal como exigió, luego meto la mano a mi bolsillo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1809
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ae079c7a:

    # "It should be okay to show her what I've been working on."
    "Creo que estará bien si le muestro en lo que he estado trabajando."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1812
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6be76278:

    # ncg neutral "What's that?" with dissolve
    ncg neutral "¿Qué es eso?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1813
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_22c32e83:

    # ks smile "This is what I'm going to be using to try and put you under."
    ks smile "Esto es lo que usaré para hipnotizarte."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1815
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8da06059:

    # "As I explain, I hold the object in my hand as she leans in to examine it."
    "Mientras explico, sostengo el objeto en mi mano y ella se inclina para examinarlo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1816
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d8e81bdb:

    # ks "It's a penlight, but I modified it a bit to make the beam a little more... attention-grabbing?"
    ks "Es una pluma linterna, pero la modifiqué un poco para que la luz... ¿capture mejor la atención?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1817
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a811d5da:

    # "Nozomi nods thoughtfully as her eyes glance over the device, before she leans back on the couch."
    "Nozomi asiente pensativamente mientras observa el dispositivo, y posteriormente vuelve a apoyarse en el sofá."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1818
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2d16651e:

    # ncg stern_closed "Okay... okay, so you'll be trying an eye-fixation induction. That's fine." with dissolve
    ncg stern_closed "De acuerdo... de acuerdo, entonces probarás una inducción de fijación ocular. Me parece bien." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1819
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9a95813d:

    # "I nod in return before clicking the penlight on and holding it so the beam shines just above her eye level."
    "Asiento en respuesta y enciendo la linterna sosteniéndola de modo que el haz brille justo por encima de la altura de sus ojos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1820
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d3bbd686:

    # ks neutral "That's right. So Nozomi, I want you to focus your gaze on the light as I shine it across your eyes."
    ks neutral "Así es. Entonces, Nozomi, quiero que enfoques tu mirada en la luz mientras la hago pasar por tus ojos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1824
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_51724481:

    # ks "Don't move your head, just sit back, relax, and watch with your eyes."
    ks "No muevas la cabeza, solo siéntate, relájate y obsérvala con tus ojos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1826
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_489e46bc:

    # "Nozomi compliantly starts to sink in the couch and puts her hands back in her lap as she begins to watch the light while I pass it across her face."
    "Nozomi obedientemente comienza a hundirse en el sofá, coloca las manos de vuelta sobre su regazo y empieza a observar la luz mientras la paso por su rostro."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1827
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b58b46ca:

    # "Now while I'm distracting her gaze with the light, I just need to speak as calmly and evenly as I can to hold her focus and induce her into a trance."
    "Ahora, mientras distraigo su mirada con la luz, solo tengo que hablar de forma calmada y nivelada, y podré mantener su atención para inducirla al trance."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1828
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_478ca0d0:

    # "I can do this..."
    "Puedo hacerlo..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1829
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_8cdc3437:

    # ks "That's right, Nozomi. Just relax and focus as the light passes back..."
    ks "Eso es, Nozomi. Solo relájate y concéntrate en la luz que va de un lado..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1832
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_a77192b8:

    # ks "And forth..."
    ks "Al otro..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1834
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2169a6ab:

    # "I wait a moment to catch her blinking, then continue."
    "Espero un momento a que parpadee, luego continúo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1835
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b6280323:

    # ks "And as you watch the light, you may start to notice yourself blinking a little more often; that your eyelids are becoming heavy and harder to keep open."
    ks "Al observar la luz, tal vez notes que parpadeas con un poco más frecuencia; que tus párpados se ponen pesados y es más difícil mantenerlos abiertos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1837
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f74a956a:

    # ks "Each time the light passes across your eyes, each time you try to catch a glimpse of the pattern you see in the light, you become a little more tired. A little more sleepy."
    ks "Cada vez que la luz pasa por tus ojos, cada vez que intentas vislumbrar el patrón que se ve en la luz, te sientes un poco más cansada. Sientes un poco más de sueño."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1839
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9220e6f9:

    # ks "It's alright to feel like this, Nozomi. It's perfectly natural to become tired while looking at the light."
    ks "Está bien sentirte así, Nozomi. Es perfectamente natural cansarte mientras miras la luz."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1841
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_bbfa8bb2:

    # ks "Relaxing more. Feeling your eyes become heavier with every blink."
    ks "Relájate más. Siente tus párpados ponerse más pesados entre más parpadeas."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1845
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2a561502:

    # ks "That's right, Nozomi. Just letting it happen." with longdissolve
    ks "Eso es, Nozomi. Déjate llevar." with longdissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1848
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_9096d2bb:

    # ks "Feeling yourself become more and more sleepy. More and more relaxed."
    ks "Cada vez más sueño. Cada vez más relajada."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1850
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_3ba09f5f:

    # ks "More and more... safe. It's perfectly safe to feel this way around the light, Nozomi."
    ks "Cada vez más... segura. Es perfectamente seguro sentirte así junto a la luz, Nozomi."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1852
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_aa853212:

    # ks "Perfectly safe and natural to let your eyelids become heavier still, as you look at the light."
    ks "Perfectamente seguro y natural sentir que tus párpados pesan aún más mientras miras la luz."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1855
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_b904ec64:

    # ks "Soon it will be impossible to look at the light, Nozomi, because you will be asleep." with longdissolve
    ks "Pronto será imposible mirar la luz, Nozomi, porque estarás dormida." with longdissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1858
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f77a7e2e:

    # ks "But that's okay."
    ks "Pero está bien."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1860
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_de678b5c:

    # ks "Keep looking into the light, Nozomi, as much as you can. Even as you continue to get sleepier."
    ks "Sigue mirando la luz, Nozomi, tanto como puedas. Aunque te siga dando sueño."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1862
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_4f7135bb:

    # ks "Getting sleepier..."
    ks "Mucho sueño..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1864
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_168ab416:

    # ks "Sleep, Nozomi."
    ks "Duerme, Nozomi."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1865
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_21e9ef23:

    # ncg sleep "..." with dissolve
    ncg sleep "..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1866
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_75da1414:

    # "It... it worked? She's really dropping at my suggestion?"
    "¿Fu-... funcionó? ¿De verdad está cayendo ante mi sugestión?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1867
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_dac80f60:

    # ks "Can you still hear me, Nozomi?"
    ks "¿Aún puedes oírme, Nozomi?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2479
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_650f3ec0:

    # ncg drooping uniform sleeptalk "Yes..." with dissolve
    ncg drooping uniform sleeptalk "Sí..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1870
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_eb0696fc:

    # "Her muted reply is music to my ears." with dissolve
    "Su silenciosa respuesta es música para mis oídos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1871
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_7cd5011e:

    # "I can hardly dare to believe it, but so far everything's going as perfectly as I imagined."
    "Apenas me atrevo a creerlo, pero hasta ahora todo va perfectamente como lo imaginé."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1872
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_e1f677b5:

    # "But I need to keep a handle on the excitement bubbling up inside me."
    "Pero tengo que contener la emoción que burbujea dentro de mí."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1873
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5a5c3225:

    # "I gotta keep my cool, and keep talking in this calm and authoritative manner I've got going on here."
    "Debo mantener la cabeza fría, y seguir hablando de forma calmada y autoritaria."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1874
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d7b6de5c:

    # ks "That's good, Nozomi. It's very important that you hear and accept what I say."
    ks "Muy bien, Nozomi. Es muy importante que escuches y aceptes todo lo que digo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1875
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_ed67f84b:

    # "Even so, I think I can take a moment to marvel at what I've just done, keeping Nozomi's phone camera pointed squarely at her peaceful-looking face."
    "Aun así, creo que puedo tomarme un momento para admirar lo que acabo de hacer, manteniendo la cámara de Nozomi apuntando directo a su pacífico rostro."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1876
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_5de76b60:

    # "As I stare at her, I have this nagging feeling that she's merely playing along with me; that she's going to jump up and call me an idiot at any moment."
    "Al mirarla, tengo un persistente sentimiento de que solo me está siguiendo la corriente; de que va a saltar y llamarme idiota en cualquier momento."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1877
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_26898621:

    # "But no, she wants this too, doesn't she? I'm sure she's taking this completely seriously."
    "Pero no, ella también quiere esto, ¿no? Estoy seguro de que se lo está tomando completamente en serio."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1878
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_6842d81a:

    # "So let's see if I can pass her a suggestion and watch how she takes it."
    "Veamos si puedo darle una sugestión y observemos qué tal la toma."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1881
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_d41561f2:

    # ks "Do you know the number four, Nozomi?"
    ks "¿Conoces el número cuatro, Nozomi?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1882
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_0924b3b7:

    # ncg "Mhm."
    ncg "Mjm."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1883
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_2f787421:

    # ks "Well, Nozomi, I want you to consider the possibility that you do not, in fact, know the number four."
    ks "Bien, Nozomi, quiero que consideres la posibilidad de que, de hecho, no conozcas el número cuatro."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1884
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_91dc085e:

    # ncg "..."
    ncg "..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1885
