translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1e651024:

    # s "I do actually believe that, or at least you think you do. It's refreshing to see this kind of earnestness from you."
    s "Eso sí lo creo, o al menos me parece que tú lo crees. Es refrescante ver esta clase de seriedad en ti."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2178
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_587cce3c:

    # "... Really? She says that like she knows me, but we've barely talked to each other before now."
    "... ¿En serio? Lo dice como si me conociera, pero apenas nos habíamos hablado hasta ahora."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2404
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_bf2a9e3c:

    # s happy "So I believe the worst case scenario here is that you will make a fool of yourself in front of me." with dissolve
    s happy "Considero que en el peor de los casos harás el ridículo enfrente de mí." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2180
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_5cbd6e11:

    # s smirk_right "The best case scenario being you talking me to sleep through the sheer tedium of your words. I could really use that nap right about now." with dissolve
    s smirk_right "En el mejor de los casos, me harás quedarme dormida con el tedio puro de tus palabras. Me vendría muy bien una siesta ahora." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2181
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_23f3c18d:

    # "Harsh. But..."
    "Qué cruel. Pero..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2182
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ac8d9d31:

    # ks surprised "S-so you're agreeing? You'll let me hypnotize you?"
    ks surprised "E-entonces, ¿aceptas? ¿Me dejarás hipnotizarte?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2183
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7f51785d:

    # s sleep "Yes. I am interested to see how you will approach this." with dissolve
    s sleep "Sí. Estoy interesada en ver el acercamiento que decides tomar." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2187
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a964a777:

    # "With a tired grunt, she sits herself down at the table."
    "Con un cansado gruñido, se sienta en la mesa."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2188
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_5a59a725:

    # scg "So, I will admit the quality of my sleep leaves much to be desired, and improving it would be useful."
    scg "Pues, admitiré que la calidad de mi sueño deja mucho que desear, y sería útil mejorarla."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2189
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c77bed69:

    # scg "And if that is our goal, then we will need to tackle the issue of my overthinking at night."
    scg "Y si ese es tu objetivo, deberíamos abordar mis problemas relacionados con pensar demasiado por la noche."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2190
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b6f57e2a:

    # ks "Overthinking?"
    ks "¿Pensar demasiado?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2191
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1c75f631:

    # scg sleep "My brain is very hard to shut down, Kyou. If you could somehow assist with that while I am attempting to sleep, it would help a great deal." with dissolve
    scg sleep "Mi cerebro es muy difícil de apagar, Kyou. Si de algún modo pudieses asistir con eso mientras intento dormir, sería de gran ayuda." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2192
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ffdeb547:

    # scg smile "But I will make this plain: I am not expecting you to succeed. I am granting you this indulgence out of sheer curiosity." with dissolve
    scg smile "Pero que quede claro: No es mi expectativa que tengas éxito. Te concedo esta indulgencia por mera curiosidad." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2193
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b78d0c5a:

    # ks frown "Right. Still, I want to do this for you."
    ks frown "Claro. Aun así, quiero hacer esto por ti."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2195
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f4f404c3:

    # "She chuckles to herself as she lays her hands flat on the table and leans back on her seat." with dissolve
    "Con una ligera risa, pone las manos sobre la mesa y se reclina contra la silla." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2196
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0b45982a:

    # scg "So shall we get started? We do not have a lot of time before I need to leave for cram school. Half an hour at most."
    scg "Pues bien, ¿comenzamos? No tenemos mucho tiempo antes de que deba irme a los cursos nocturnos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2197
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_afdb3436:

    # "That really doesn't sound like enough time for something like this. Geez."
    "Eso no suena a tiempo suficiente para algo como esto. Caray."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2198
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4b9a8de8:

    # scg "I assume I need to take a relaxed position, but besides that I am relying on your direction, Kyou."
    scg "Asumo que debo adoptar una posición relajada, pero más allá de eso, espero tu dirección, Kyou."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2199
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_45996a14:

    # "... She's being surprisingly chill about this. Especially after what she was telling me about malicious hypnotists and the like."
    "... Está sorprendentemente tranquila con esto. Sobre todo, tras haberme contado sobre hipnotistas maliciosos y todas esas cosas."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2200
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_15a30ddb:

    # "So it feels like despite everything she does actually trust me for this."
    "Me da la sensación de que, a pesar de todo, de verdad confía en mí para hacer esto."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2203
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_93324efa:

    # "And it makes me feel like I can trust her in return."
    "Y me hace sentir que yo puedo confiar en ella."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2777
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e3fd2201:

    # scg stern "What is that? What are you doing?" with dissolve
    scg stern "¿Qué es eso? ¿Qué estás haciendo?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2205
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_81568424:

    # ks smile "This is what we're going to be using to hypnotize you today. I designed it myself."
    ks smile "Esto es lo que estaremos usando para hipnotizarte hoy. Yo mismo la diseñé."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2206
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_661bd78c:

    # ks "It's meant to help you focus and let you slip into a trance more easily."
    ks "Tiene el objetivo de ayudarte a concentrarte y permitirte entrar más fácilmente al trance."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2207
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_963bd356:

    # ks "And since we don't have a lot of time I reckon it'll be really useful today."
    ks "Y como no tenemos mucho tiempo, estimo que será muy útil hoy."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2782
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0577a432:

    # "Sayori nods slowly." with dissolve
    "Sayori asiente lentamente." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2209
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_77f69fd1:

    # scg "Okay... that raises some questions concerning that, but they can wait for another time."
    scg "Está bien... eso genera algunas preguntas al respecto, pero pueden esperar para después."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2211
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_88f5febb:

    # "I give my best attempt at an assured smile as I hold the penlight above her head and switch it on."
    "Intento mostrar una sonrisa segura al sostener la linterna sobre su cabeza y encenderla."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2212
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b5040bc7:

    # ks "Great. So if you could stare straight ahead, then look up towards the light with just your eyes?"
    ks "Genial. Entonces, ¿podrías mirar hacia adelante, luego voltear a ver la luz solo con tus ojos?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2218
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c0135759:

    # "As I watch her comply, I carefully turn the penlight so that its light passes across her eyes."
    "La veo seguir las instrucciones, y con cuidado muevo la linterna para hacer la luz pasar por sus ojos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2219
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_161663d6:

    # ks neutral "That's right, just like that."
    ks neutral "Eso es, justo así."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2222
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_bfa9e52c:

    # "As I drag the beam across her eyes again I notice her mouth falling open as she lets out a muted gasp." with dissolve
    "Arrastro el haz por sus ojos y noto cómo su boca se abre de repente, soltando un ahogado jadeo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2881
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_11891012:

    # ks confused "... Are you alright?"
    ks confused "... ¿Te encuentras bien?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2225
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_fb4bd51b:

    # "Sayori blinks firmly a couple of times and nods her head before opening her eyes again." with dissolve
    "Sayori parpadea firmemente un par de veces y asiente, para luego volver a abrir los ojos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2226
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_44c14b97:

    # scg neutral "I am fine. Continue." with dissolve
    scg neutral "Estoy bien. Prosigue." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2228
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4768667e:

    # "I wait a moment for her to look back up, then pass the light across her eyes again." with dissolve
    "Espero un momento a que mire otra vez hacia arriba, luego vuelvo a pasar la luz por sus ojos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2230
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0df1ff17:

    # ks neutral "Just sitting calmly and looking up at the light as you take a deep breath, in and out. That's all you need to do."
    ks neutral "Solo siéntate tranquilamente y mira la luz mientras respiras profundo. Inhala y exhala. Solo eso debes hacer."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2232
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_e772e035:

    # ks "And as you look, you may find yourself straining a little to keep your eyes up and staring into the light."
    ks "Y al mirar, puede que te tome algo de esfuerzo mantener la vista arriba y observar la luz."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2234
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_08137b39:

    # ks "That's natural, that's fine, just keep looking. Breathing in deep."
    ks "Es natural, está bien, solo sigue mirando. Inhala profundo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2236
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b78e985e:

    # ks "Even if you feel the muscles in your eyes continue to strain, and even if you feel your eyelids begin to flutter closed as they become heavy. And exhale..."
    ks "Aunque sientas que los músculos de tus ojos se cansan, y aunque sientas tus párpados intentando cerrarse y ponerse más pesados. Y exhala..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2238
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_02f8281b:

    # ks "It's all fine. All you need to do is keep looking at the light. And breathe in."
    ks "Está todo bien. Solo necesitas seguir mirando la luz. E inhala."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2240
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f0041ee6:

    # ks "You may even find, every time you blink, that those eyelids of yours are gaining more and more weight. And now breathe out."
    ks "Puede que, con cada pestañeo, esos párpados ganen más y más peso. Y ahora, exhala."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2242
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_77e08c57:

    # ks "But all you need to do, Sayori, is to keep looking up at the light. Just relaxing. And looking. And breathe in."
    ks "Pero todo lo que tienes que hacer, Sayori, es seguir mirando la luz. Solo relájate. Y observa. E inhala."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2244
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_dd29659f:

    # ks "Looking and relaxing. Breathe out."
    ks "Observa y relájate. Exhala."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2473
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9f4a326c:

    # "... Is it working? Or is she just about to take a regular nap in front of me?"
    "... ¿Está funcionando? ¿O solo está a punto de tomar otra siesta frente a mí?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2248
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_67932da8:

    # "Either way, she's definitely finding it harder to stare up as her eyes are illuminated over and over. I'll keep going."
    "En cualquier caso, definitivamente le es más difícil mirar hacia arriba mientras sus párpados son alumbrados una y otra vez. Seguiré así."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2250
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_388e57e9:

    # ks "That's right, Sayori. Still looking at the light. That's all you need to do. Breathe in."
    ks "Eso es, Sayori. Sigue mirando la luz. Solo eso tienes que hacer. Inhala."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2252
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_09b13536:

    # ks "You may even find that your eyelids have become so heavy that you can't even open them anymore. Breathe out."
    ks "Puede que tus párpados estén tan pesados que ya ni siquiera puedas abrirlos. Exhala."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2482
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_1b6b6647:

    # ks "But, Sayori, all you need to do is look. Breathe in, and perhaps you can open them again just once more."
    ks "Pero, Sayori, todo lo que tienes que hacer es mirar. Inhala, y tal vez puedas abrirlos solo una vez más."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2485
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0200cda7:

    # ks "Very good, Sayori. Just looking at the light."
    ks "Muy bien, Sayori. Solo mira la luz."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2259
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f30a83be:

    # ks "And now closing your eyes and... Breathe out. Sleep."
    ks "Y ahora cierra los ojos y... Exhala. Duerme."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2491
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_d5450211:

    # scg "..."
    scg "..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2263
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_8d36cad0:

    # "I watch as she slumps forward, her head dropping as it comes to join her arms at rest on the table."
    "La veo desplomarse hacia adelante, su cabeza cae para descansar entre sus brazos sobre la mesa."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2264
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4b4ed9e2:

    # "Did that do it? Even without my doubts it's so hard to tell with her if she's really hypnotically asleep... or just asleep."
    "¿Habrá servido? Con ella es muy difícil diferenciar si de verdad está durmiendo hipnóticamente... o solo durmiendo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2265
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_69e1187a:

    # "I'll just carry on as if she really is hypnotized. That's the best thing to do right now."
    "Solo continuaré como si realmente estuviera hipnotizada. Creo que será lo mejor en este momento."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2266
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_19fbb539:

    # ks "That's right, Sayori. Deep asleep now. Just breathing in and out, feeling so very relaxed."
    ks "Eso es, Sayori. Duerme profundamente. Inhala y exhala, sintiéndote muy, muy relajada."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2267
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_98b4881d:

    # "Quietly sneaking around to her side of the table, I quickly check her to make sure she doesn't look uncomfortable resting like that."
    "Escabulléndome silenciosamente a su lado de la mesa, rápidamente la reviso para asegurarme de que no luzca incómoda reposando así."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2268
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_eb008b3c:

    # "I think she'll be fine."
    "Creo que estará bien."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2269
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_2e604489:

    # ks "And as deeply relaxed, and as deeply hypnotized as you are, you will find you can still listen to and answer any questions I have."
    ks "Y estando tan relajada, tan profundamente hipnotizada, nota que aún puedes escuchar y responder cualquiera de mis preguntas."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2270
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_3aaa55bf:

    # ks "In fact, every time you answer, you will find yourself going even deeper into trance, knowing just how deeply hypnotized you are."
    ks "De hecho, cada vez que contestes, encontrarás que caes más profundo en este trance, siendo solo consciente de lo profundamente hipnotizada que estás."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2271
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6cbdd3cd:

    # ks "Do you understand, Sayori?"
    ks "¿Comprendes, Sayori?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2272
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4a921b70:

    # scg "... Uh-huh."
    scg "... Ajá."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2274
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c89e19e1:

    # "I'm a little relieved to hear her speak. She might still be messing with me, but somehow I don't think she would."
    "Estoy un poco aliviado de escucharla hablar. Puede que me esté tomando el pelo, pero creo que ella no haría eso."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2275
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a69becbc:

    # ks "Very good, Sayori. Feeling yourself going deeper. Feeling all your thoughts, your cares, your worries, all of them fading away as you go so nice and deep for me."
    ks "Muy bien, Sayori. Siente cómo caes más profundo. Siente todos tus pensamientos, todas tus preocupaciones, todas desvaneciéndose mientras caes más profundo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2276
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9c50127f:

    # ks "Because that's what you want while you're asleep, isn't it? To let your mind go blank; empty of thought and worry?"
    ks "Porque eso es lo único que quieres cuando duermes, ¿no es así? ¿Poner la mente en blanco; vaciarla de todo pensamiento y preocupación?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2277
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f71589c7:

    # scg "Y... y-yes..."
    scg "S... s-sí..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2279
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_72308236:

    # "A bit of hesitation there. I guess for someone like her, the idea of her losing her thoughts, even for a little while, could be a bit scary."
    "Un poco de indecisión. Supongo que, para alguien como ella, la idea de perder sus pensamientos, incluso por un rato, puede dar algo de miedo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2280
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_988c6200:

    # ks "That's right, Sayori. Going deeper now. Letting your mind become blank. Empty. Vacant."
    ks "Eso es, Sayori. Caes más profundo. Deja que tu mente quede en blanco. Vacía. Libre."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2281
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_65aa02cd:

    # ks "Finding it so easy to lose every thought in your head. Finding it so easy to become mindless and blank."
    ks "Verás que es muy fácil vaciar todo pensamiento de tu cabeza. Es muy fácil apagar por completo tu mente."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2282
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_b774d74a:

    # ks "So easy in fact, that whenever you are about to go to sleep at night, you will find yourself effortlessly returning to this blank, mindless, completely relaxed state."
    ks "De hecho, es tan fácil que cada vez que estés a punto de irte a dormir, podrás regresar sin esfuerzo a este estado en blanco, sin pensamientos, completamente relajada."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2283
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ccc56104:

    # ks "You will be able to do it so effortlessly, that you will not even have to think of doing it."
    ks "Serás capaz de hacerlo con tan poco esfuerzo, que ni siquiera tendrás que pensar en ello."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2284
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7398adcb:

    # ks "You will automatically return to this blank, empty and mindless state you are in now, whenever you are safely in bed at night and you are about to go to sleep."
    ks "Tu mente de forma automática estará de nuevo en blanco y vacía como ahora, siempre que estés segura en tu cama y estés a punto de irte a dormir."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2285
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_6cbdd3cd_1:

    # ks "Do you understand, Sayori?"
    ks "¿Comprendes, Sayori?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2286
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_bdf91b55:

    # scg "Understand..."
    scg "Comprendo..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2288
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_77a077f2:

    # ks "Very good, Sayori. Going deeper still. Letting this all become a very real, very true part of who you are."
    ks "Muy bien, Sayori. Caes todavía más profundo. Deja que todo esto se vuelva real, parte de quien eres."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2289
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9da0f730:

    # "I take a quick look at my phone... Has it already been half an hour? Goddamn."
    "Le echo un rápido vistazo a mi teléfono... ¿Ya paso media hora? Maldición."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2290
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9e5b0df6:

    # ks "And in a few moments, we are going to wake you up. I am going to count to five, and on five you will awaken feeling happy and refreshed."
    ks "En unos momentos, vamos despertarte. Contaré hasta cinco, y a la cuenta de cinco vas a despertar sintiéndote fresca y feliz."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2291
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_f52f2d62:

    # ks "Counting now... one."
    ks "Contaré ahora... uno."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2292
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_dc84d1a1:

    # ks "Two, slowly starting to feel your thoughts returning."
    ks "Dos, siente cómo tus pensamientos regresan lentamente."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2294
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_fc207132:

    # ks "Three, letting the strength come back to your arms and legs."
    ks "Tres, la fuerza regresas a tus brazos y piernas."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2295
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_55fb3097:

    # ks "Four, testing your eyelids, feeling them become light once again."
    ks "Cuatro, mueve un poco los párpados, siente cómo se ponen cada vez más ligeros."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2296
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ce8b1b19:

    # ks "And five. Wide awake, refreshed and happy."
    ks "Y cinco. Despierta, fresca y contenta."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2297
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ca8795a2:

    # scg uniform drowsy "Mmn..." with longdissolve
    scg uniform drowsy "Mmn..." with longdissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2299
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_7caf9e10:

    # "Sayori weakly lifts her head from the table, yawning quietly as she arches her back."
    "Sayori levanta débilmente la cabeza de la mesa, bostezando mientras arquea su espalda."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2300
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ce075668:

    # scg "Sorry, Kyou. I was not actually trying to nap."
    scg "Lo siento, Kyou. No era mi intención tomar una siesta."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2301
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_96c39965:

    # scg "I may be more tired than I thought."
    scg "Puede que esté más cansada de lo que pensé."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2302
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_4c902cd5:

    # "I chuckle and shake my head at her."
    "Río un poco y sacudo la cabeza."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2303
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_bf2e6acd:

    # ks smile "I dunno, Sayori. From where I'm standing I think that went really well."
    ks smile "No lo sé, Sayori. Desde mi punto de vista, creo que salió muy bien."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2309
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_9672bc49:

    # "She pulls herself up out of her chair with a moan and glances up at the clock in the room."
    "Se remueve el cabello de la cara y con un quejido mira en dirección al reloj de la pared."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2312
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_a05cbe87:

    # s panicked_right "Wait, is that the time?" with dissolve
    s panicked_right "Espera, ¿esa es la hora?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2997
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_eb500d94:

    # ks confused "Uhh... yeah, that clock's right."
    ks confused "Eeh... sí, el reloj está correcto."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2314
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_965ab953:

    # "With a gasp, Sayori hastily grabs at her things and makes a beeline for the door."
    "Con un jadeo, Sayori toma precipitadamente sus cosas y se va directo a la puerta."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2318
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_96ff4a46:

    # s "I have to go."
    s "Me tengo que ir."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2319
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_ea21cf27:

    # "... I don't think I've ever seen her move that fast."
    "... Creo que nunca la vi moverse tan rápido."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2322
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_68ebbf32:

    # "And what the hell?! Don't I even get a thank you?"
    "¡¿Y qué demonios?! ¿Ni siquiera recibo un \"gracias\"?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2326
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_57f165bb:

    # "I mean yeah, okay she was running late for cram school, but I'm sure it wouldn't have killed her to talk through what we did first."
    "Es decir, sí, de acuerdo, se le está haciendo tarde para sus cursos nocturnos, pero seguro no la habría matado decir algo de lo que hicimos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2327
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_cc1b4bdd:

    # "Kinda feels ungrateful on her part."
    "Se siente un poco malagradecido de su parte."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2328
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_c179ec3c:

    # "Did it work, though? She sure looked like she was aware enough to listen for the whole session we did, and didn't just sleep it off."
    "Aunque, ¿funcionó? Parece que estaba lo bastante consciente como para escuchar durante toda la sesión, y no se quedó dormida."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2329
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_69144ed1:

    # "I'd call her if I had her number. I NEED to know how my penlight worked. Whether my hypnotic routine was worth a shit."
    "La llamaría si tuviera su número. NECESITO saber qué tal funcionó mi linterna. O si mi rutina hipnótica valió una mierda."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2330
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Sayori_0061bf05:

    # "I can't believe she left me in the lurch like this."
    "No puedo creer que me haya dejado en la estacada así."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2336
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_9471698f:

    # "If yesterday's classes were boring, today's are just torture."
    "Si las clases de ayer fueron aburridas, las de hoy son una tortura."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2338
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_cc7f232b:

    # "I'm in just no mood for this shit at all. Who fucking cares?"
    "No estoy de humor para esta mierda. ¿A quién carajo le importa?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2341
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_6195b600:

    # "At the sound of the lunch bell I look to Nozomi and her group seated towards the front of the class."
    "Al sonar la campana del almuerzo, miro a Nozomi y su grupo sentadas al frente de la clase."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2348
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_79f6d329:

    # h "Did someone say \"Rooftop lunch\"?"
    h "¿Alguien dijo \"Almuerzo en la azotea\"?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2349
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_44b2a5a8:

    # s smile_right "No. There must be something wrong with your ears." with dissolve
    s smile_right "No. Algo debe andar mal con tus oídos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2350
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_47e12d66:

    # h uniform_armup happy "Eh, your faces were sayin' it~" with dissolve
    h uniform_armup happy "Eh, sus rostros lo decían..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2351
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_8bc207ec:

    # n frown_side "Hmm..." with dissolve
    n frown_side "Mmm..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2352
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_4e18d47a:

    # n smile_side "Sure, let's do it." with dissolve
    n smile_side "Claro, hagámoslo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2357
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_60fde725:

    # "I watch those three disappear, then pull out my packed lunch and settle in for another afternoon alone."
    "Veo a esas tres desaparecer, luego saco mi lonchera y me preparo para pasar otra tarde solo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2358
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_a59328e3:

    # "This is just how it's always been. But, damn, I had high hopes for this week."
    "Así es como siempre ha sido. Pero, demonios, tenía muchas esperanzas para esta semana."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2359
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_5a81cd27:

    # "Figures Hiroko would be the one to bring me down to earth..."
    "Y pensar que Hiroko volvería a ponerme los pies en la tierra..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2362
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_8f89cb83:

    # "After what feels like aeons, the regular school day comes to an end."
    "Tras lo que parecieron eones, este día común y corriente de escuela llega a su fin."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2363
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_dd30a599:

    # "Just have to do cleaning duties and I can go home and put another shitty day to bed."
    "Solo queda la limpieza y podré irme a casa y concluir otro día de mierda en mi cama."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2365
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_2c4c153c:

    # "Today it's my turn to clean the hallway with a few other people."
    "Hoy es mi turno de limpiar el pasillo con unas cuantas personas más."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2367
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_2d400264:

    # "Including Hiroko, apparently. Although she usually pairs with someone else when we're on cleaning duty together." with dissolve
    "Incluyendo a Hiroko, al parecer. Aunque ella suele juntarse con cualquier otra persona cuando nos toca la limpieza juntos." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2368
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_9ddedc9a:

    # h "Watch me play today."
    h "Ven a verme jugar hoy."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:3087
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_6a50e583:

    # ks confused "Eh? Haven't you seen enough of me for one week?"
    ks confused "¿Eh? ¿No me has visto suficiente para una semana?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2370
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_80401106:

    # h annoyed_side "Well, yeah." with dissolve
    h annoyed_side "Bueno, sí." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2371
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_306f6306:

    # "There's a pause as we both wring out our cleaning cloths and crouch down on the floor ready to sweep across it."
    "Hay una pausa mientras ambos exprimimos nuestros pañuelos y nos agachamos, listos para limpiar el suelo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2971
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_2bafc081:

    # h uniform_headhold2 "But I get it. You wanna see if you did anything." with dissolve
    h uniform_headhold2 "Pero, entiendo. Quieres ver si todo eso hizo algo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2373
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_d06bed20:

    # ks neutral "Do you... feel any different?"
    ks neutral "¿Te... sientes diferente?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2374
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_f193f432:

    # h sleeptalk "Nope." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Nop." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2377
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_9ce86f32:

    # "And with that we bound across the hall from end to end, leaving a trail of clean, wet floor in our wake." with shake
    "Y entonces, recorremos todo el pasillo de principio a fin, dejando un rastro de suelo limpio y mojado a nuestro paso." with shake

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2378
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_c243305f:

    # h "Was I s'posed to?"
    h "¿Qué se supone que pase?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2379
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_181cb4ed:

    # ks frown "I don't know..."
    ks frown "No lo sé..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2380
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_87d6ed7e:

    # h irritated vein "You don't? Some hypnotist you are." with dissolve
    h irritated vein "¿No lo sabes? Qué buen hipnotista saliste." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2381
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_b5af829e:

    # ks "Yeah, well it's the first time I- {w=0.8}{nw}"
    ks "Sí, pues es la primera vez que- {w=0.8}{nw}"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2385
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_bca72c19:

    # "Hiroko doesn't wait as she runs the cloth across the floor back the way we came, leaving me talking to her backside before I awkwardly start my own run." with shake
    "Hiroko no espera y recorre el suelo con el pañuelo de regreso por donde vinimos, dejándome hablando con su espalda antes de empezar yo mismo a correr." with shake

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2387
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_3bebd8ee:

    # "As I catch up with her, she stands and tosses her cloth into a bucket of lukewarm water." with dissolve
    "Cuando la alcanzo, ella se levanta y arroja su su pañuelo a una cubeta de agua tibia." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2388
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_6153ce42:

    # h "Well, whatevs. Come with."
    h "Bueno, como sea. Solo ven."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2389
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_aa192c96:

    # "I sigh and shrug my shoulders."
    "Suspiro y me encojo de hombros."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2390
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_8507104a:

    # ks "Fine, fine."
    ks "Está bien, está bien."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2393
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_bcc039ae:

    # "And so after class lets out I find myself once again trudging over to the tennis courts."
    "Y así, después de las clases me encuentro una vez más caminando penosamente por las canchas de tenis."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2394
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_ddc0b09d:

    # "While Hiroko goes to get changed I have to wonder why she bothered to invite me back here."
    "Mientras que Hiroko va a cambiarse, me paro a preguntarme por qué se molestó en invitarme de regreso aquí."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2395
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_b367bfbe:

    # "Does she think I actually did something? Or is she just humoring me now?"
    "¿Cree que de verdad hice algo? ¿O solo es para seguirme la corriente?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2399
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_8cd07b35:

    # "I'm not left to ponder over it for too long as Hiroko soon re-emerges, with some other girl in tow." with dissolve
    "No paso mucho tiempo reflexionándolo, pues Hiroko pronto reemerge, con otra chica detrás de ella." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2400
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_29bd33b9:

    # "I don't really know her, just that she's some friend of Hiroko's. I see them hang out together sometimes."
    "No la conozco, solo sé que es amiga de Hiroko. A veces las veo pasar tiempo juntas."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2401
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_f0d4c9a5:

    # "In any case, she's not the one Hiroko played off the court yesterday."
    "De cualquier forma, no es la chica con la que Hiroko jugó ayer."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2402
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_27908fb8:

    # h "Risa, you know this dude?"
    h "Risa, ¿conoces a este tipo?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2403
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_63c32dba:

    # r neutral_side "Isn't that the creeper from your class?" with dissolve
    r neutral_side "¿No es el chico espeluznante de tu clase?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2404
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_49781b01:

    # ks frown "Hey!"
    ks frown "¡Oye!"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2405
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_ac78f185:

    # h annoyed "Yeah, that one." with dissolve
    h annoyed "Síp, ese." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2407
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_258dd7b3:

    # ks "What are you telling people about me, Hiroko?" with dissolve
    ks "¿Qué es lo que le dices a la gente sobre mí, Hiroko?" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2408
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_3c2129db:

    # h frown "Just what they need to know." with dissolve
    h frown "Solo lo que necesitan saber." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2409
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_3c8fe955:

    # "She turns back to her playing partner."
    "Vuelve a mirar a su compañera de juego."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:3011
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_903122df:

    # h tennis_armup angry_side "Anyway, you wanna play a set? Yesterday was a bust without you and I NEED a proper fuckin' game around here." with dissolve
    h tennis_armup angry_side "Como sea, ¿quieres jugar un set? Ayer sin ti fue una decepción y NECESITO un puto juego de verdad." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2454
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_fadbbf35:

    # r wristband_left_armup tennis_armup grin "I hear that! Let's do it." with dissolve
    r wristband_left_armup tennis_armup grin "¡Entendido! Hay que hacerlo." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2414
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_729bf32e:

    # ks sigh "And you expect me to just watch this?"
    ks sigh "¿Y esperas que me quede aquí a ver esto?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:3014
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_91547fc7:

    # h tennis_headhold2 frown "'Course not. I mean..." with dissolve
    h tennis_headhold2 frown "Claro que no. Es que..." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2417
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_e82456f3:

    # h smirk "We need a ball boy." with dissolve
    h smirk "Necesitamos un recogepelotas." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2418
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_1b643d4a:

    # ks frown "Screw you."
    ks frown "Vete al diablo."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2420
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_ad282e91:

    # "Hiroko gives a nonchalant shrug." with dissolve
    "Hiroko me encoge los hombros despreocupadamente." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2421
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_b5460d5a:

    # h "Suit yourself. Just watch me, 'kay?"
    h "Haz lo que quieras. Solo obsérvame, ¿bien?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2424
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_1084028a:

    # "As she and Risa move onto the court to start their warm-ups, a thought strikes me." with dissolve
    "Mientras ella y Risa entran a la cancha para comenzar a calentar, un pensamiento me golpea." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2425
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_182b40b4:

    # "Hiroko basically just gave me permission to stare at her?"
    "¿Hiroko básicamente me dio permiso de mirarla?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2426
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_23508910:

    # "After chastising me so many times for looking at girls, that sounds like such a weird thing for her to say to me."
    "Después de reprenderme tantas veces por mirar chicas lindas, parece muy raro que me diga eso."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2428
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_7f990744:

    # ks "That looked out to me!"
    ks "¡Me parece que eso fue fuera!"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2429
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_4b1d55e2:

    # r "Yeah, Hiro, that was wide. Fifteen thirty."
    r "Sí, Hiroko, la lanzaste muy lejos. Quince a treinta."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2430
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_468cdeee:

    # h "Shit..."
    h "Mierda..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2432
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_ec4652eb:

    # "I look across as Hiroko moodily bounces another ball by her feet."
    "Miro a la distancia mientras Hiroko rebota malhumoradamente otra pelota junto a sus pies."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2433
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_f6012472:

    # "They've been going at it for about twenty minutes now at two games all."
    "Han jugado por unos veinte minutos y llevan dos juegos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2434
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_becefcbb:

    # "Despite my earlier reluctance I've been gathering their spent balls in-between points and acting as a makeshift line judge, just for something to do."
    "A pesar de mi reluctancia de hace rato, he estado reuniendo las pelotas usadas entre puntos y actuando como un juez improvisado, solo para tener algo que hacer."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2435
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_fcc3678b:

    # "But when I do spectate, it's mostly to look at the pink-haired bundle of wrath currently on serve."
    "Pero cuando sí observo, es mayormente para ver al manojo de ira pelirrosa que está sirviendo en este momento."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2437
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_5c1e39d5:

    # "I watch as she tosses the ball vertically up in the air, coils her body and brings her racket down with a crack."
    "La veo arrojar la pelota hacia arriba, enrollar su cuerpo y golpearla firmemente con la raqueta."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2438
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_2dd06cc6:

    # "... sending the ball crashing hard against the net."
    "... enviando la bola a estrellarse con fuerza contra la red."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2439
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_26e1f3a6:

    # r "Oof. Bit off your game tonight, huh, Hiro."
    r "Uf. Un poco fuera de forma esta noche, ¿eh, Hiro?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2440
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_1ba5c604:

    # "I notice Hiroko scowl for a second, but by the time I've tossed the ball back to her it's all but disappeared."
    "Noto un ceño fruncido en el rostro de Hiroko por un segundo, pero para cuando le arrojo la bola de regreso ya ha desaparecido."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2442
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_e993bc23:

    # "Once more she sends the ball up into the air and makes her serve, this time sending it towards the inside line."
    "Una vez más, eleva la pelota en el aire y hace un servicio, enviándola esta vez a la línea central."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2444
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_6d20866e:

    # "Risa anticipates this play and returns it with a solid backhand, sending Hiroko into a sprint to make a backhanded return of her own."
    "Risa anticipa esta jugada y la devuelve con un sólido revés, mandando a Hiroko a correr para responder con otro revés de su parte."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2445
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_c5dd02de:

    # "She makes it, running with her racket out full-length as she grips it tightly with both hands."
    "Logra llegar, corriendo y estirando su raqueta al máximo, sosteniéndola con fuerza con ambas manos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2447
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_6248e5b5:

    # "It didn't look like a clean hit, but it's enough to send it over the net and flying across court, leaving Risa stranded."
    "No pareció un golpe limpio, pero es suficiente para enviarla por encima de la red y hacerla sobrevolar la cancha, dejando a Risa varada."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2448
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_a37b9d25:

    # "And as I look from Risa to the ball, I see it bounce just inside the line. Huh."
    "Y pasando mi mirada de Risa a la pelota, veo esta última rebotar apenas adentro de la línea. Vaya."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2451
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_9c04a281:

    # r "Out!" with dissolve
    r "¡Fuera!" with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2452
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_21a320ab:

    # ks surprised "Wha?"
    ks surprised "¿Qué?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2494
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_e0f9314a:

    # r tennis_armup wristband_left_armup frown "That was totally out! My point." with dissolve
    r tennis_armup wristband_left_armup frown "Eso definitivamente fue fuera. Punto para mí." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2454
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_71c65ac2:

    # ks angry "I was standing right here! I saw it land in!"
    ks angry "¡Yo estaba parado justo aquí! ¡La vi caer adentro!"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2455
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_896f8610:

    # "I frown and point to where I'd seen it bounce."
    "Frunzo el ceño y señalo a donde la vi rebotar."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2456
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_5316a038:

    # "It's not like I give a shit, really, but I know what I saw."
    "No es que me importe una mierda, pero sé lo que vi."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2498
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_86156d61:

    # r frown_side "Don't play favourites, ball boy. Hiro, it was out." with dissolve
    r frown_side "No seas favoritista, recogepelotas. Hiro, fue fuera." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2458
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_49310789:

    # "... I kind of expected Hiroko to blow up by now."
    "... Esperaba que Hiroko ya hubiera explotado."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2459
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_c7f27ded:

    # "Even if she didn't get as clear a view as I did, she must have thought she landed it too. At least enough to argue over it."
    "Aunque no tuvo una vista tan clara como la mía, también debió pensar que aterrizó bien. Al menos lo suficiente como para discutir."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2462
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_95e42459:

    # "But as I look to her, she merely shrugs and walks across the baseline while holding her hand out for me to toss her a ball." with dissolve
    "Pero cuando la miro, simplemente se encoge de hombros y camina por la línea de fondo, extendiendo la mano para que le pase la pelota." with dissolve

# game/kyou 2.rpy:2463
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Hiroko_4ca2afb5:

    # h tennis_armup "Fifteen forty. Let's go!" with dissolve
