# game/kyou 2.rpy:749
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_8594c543:

    # ks sigh "So uh... This is my house."
    ks sigh "Pues, eh... Esta es mi casa."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:763
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_061250ee:

    # "He takes her down, and instructs her to lose all the suggestions he planted in her head earlier."
    "La pone en trance y le ordena que pierda todas las sugestiones que sembró en su cabeza."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:764
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_c59b7297:

    # "After that... The thought crosses his mind that Hiroko is NOT going to handle this well."
    "Después de eso... Se le cruza por la mente que Hiroko NO se tomará bien todo esto."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:765
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_9080c267:

    # "Maybe if we could just pretend all this never happened?"
    "¿Tal vez podamos fingir que esto nunca pasó?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:766
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_e7609da9:

    # "If he can alter entire facets of her personality, he's sure Hiroko would just suppress the memory of this whole shitshow if he asked her to."
    "Si puede alterar facetas enteras de su personalidad, de seguro Hiroko suprimiría los recuerdos de toda esta mierda si se lo pidiera."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:767
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_bc7ac4b9:

    # "No harm done, right?"
    "Sin daños, ¿verdad?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:772
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_7277213e:

    # "Kyou reasons that using hypnosis to fix his problems got everyone in this mess to begin with."
    "Kyou razona que usar la hipnosis para resolver sus problemas los metió a todos en este desastre en primer lugar."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:773
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_8f9a6579:

    # "So no, he'll just have Hiroko wake slowly having simply lifted all his suggestions from her mind...."
    "Así que, no, solo despertará a Hiroko lentamente, habiendo simplemente removido las sugestiones de su mente..."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:778
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_b471e047:

    # "She sets upon him with a roar, throwing punch after punch while screaming at him to stay out of her head." with vpunch
    "Ella se abalanza contra él con un rugido, un puñetazo tras otro mientras grita que no se atreba a entrar a su cabeza." with vpunch

# game/kyou 2.rpy:780
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_9bb7a50b:

    # "Let's go all drama for this. Kyou stumbles to the floor and just takes his punishment while Hiroko thumps his chest as she breaks down sobbing." with shake
    "Todo es drama. Kyou cae al suelo se queda a recibir su castigo mientras Hiroko golpea su pecho rompiendo en sollozos." with shake

# game/kyou 2.rpy:781
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_22af1072:

    # "He's not that badly hurt though, as Hiroko doesn't pack a lot of venom beyond the first couple punches while her mind is still reeling from the experience."
    "No queda muy lastimado, pues Hiroko no tiene energía suficiente más que para los primeros golpes mientras su mente sigue tambaleándose por la experiencia."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:782
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_f88da1df:

    # "To say nothing of the fact that she kinda understands that he released her and she's no longer in immediate danger."
    "Sin mencionar el hecho de que comprende que él la liberó y que ya no se encuentra en peligro."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:783
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_75cbc3c7:

    # "So after exhausting herself, Kyou offers another apology and Hiroko tries to explain how it felt to be brainwashed by Kyou's penlight."
    "Así que, una vez se agota, Kyou le ofrece otra disculpa y Hiroko intenta explicar cómo se sintió tener el cerebro lavado por la linterna de Kyou."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:784
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_90ddb022:

    # "How she couldn't resist and it felt so good to just go along with it yadda yadda."
    "Cómo no pudo resistir y se sintió tan bien solo seguir la corriente; bla, bla, bla."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:785
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_ba11f422:

    # "That she couldn't even acknowledge how fucked up and helpless she was until Kyou woke her up. She was basically his to command."
    "Que no pudo reconocer lo jodida e indefensa que estaba hasta que Kyou la despertó. Básicamente estaba a sus órdenes."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:786
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_cc755cd2:

    # "It's proven Hiroko's fears about her vaguely creepy classmate in ways she never would've imagined."
    "Eso demuestra el miedo de Hiroko hacia el bicho raro de su clase de formas que nunca habría imaginado."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:787
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_c1fca703:

    # "For his part, Kyou mostly just lets her get it all out while he listens, but bristles at being called a creep again."
    "En esta parte, Kyou mayormente permite que ella lo saque todo y escucha, pero se eriza al volver ser llamado bicho raro."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:788
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_327f0642:

    # "So then Kyou, why did you basically make Hiroko into some kind of slave/robot? (we'll probably branch both \"What have I done?\" paths into the same place)"
    "Entonces, Kyou, ¿por qué básicamente convertiste a Hiroko en una especie de esclava/robot? (Probablemente ramifiquemos los dos senderos de \"¿Qué he hecho?\" al mismo lugar)"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:789
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_88ece8c9:

    # "You wanna answer that, Kyou, you fucking perv?"
    "¿Vas a contestar a eso, Kyou, pervertido de mierda?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:790
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_467af4ce:

    # "And Kyou is like, okay he was mad at Hiroko for falsely accusing him and trying to pick a fight, so maybe he wasn't thinking so much himself when he actually put her under."
    "Y Kyou dice algo como: muy bien, estaba molesto con Hiroko por acusarlo falsamente e intentar buscar pelea, así que probablemente no pensó claramente cuando la hipnotizó."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:791
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_ece89fc1:

    # "But if he was really as bad as she thinks, she'd still be giggling and fawning over him right now wouldn't she?"
    "Pero si fuera tan malo como ella cree, seguiría riendo y adulándolo justo ahora, ¿no?"

# game/kyou 2.rpy:793
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_1901b5c7:

    # "She concedes the point, but it hardly makes her feel better. She feels completely violated, and Nozomi must feel the same."
    "Le concede ese punto, pero no la hace sentir mucho mejor. Se siente completamente violada, y Nozomi debe sentirse igual."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:794
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_0f90d04b:

    # "No wonder she didn't want to talk about this. It all sounds completely nuts if Hiroko hadn't experienced this for herself."
    "Con razón no quería hablar de esto. Sonaría descabellado si Hiroko no lo hubiera experimentado por sí misma."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:795
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_74e3943e:

    # "... And now that she's steered the topic to Nozomi, Hiroko comes to the conclusion that her bestie needs her now more than ever."
    "... Y ahora que toca el tema de Nozomi, Hiroko llega a la conclusión de que su mejor amiga la necesita más que nunca."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:797
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_cc2836e5:

    # "So she dashes out of the house, but not before yelling at Kyou to stay the fuck away from them both."
    "Así que sale corriendo de la casa, no sin antes gritarle a Kyou que se aleje a la mierda de las dos."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:798
translate spanish Day2_Villain_Kyou_7e78feac:

    # "Kyou will probably yell he's sorry as she leaves, for all the good that seems to do."
    "Kyou probablemente le grite que lo siente cuando se va, por más que no parezca ayudar mucho."

# game/kyou 2.rpy:1662
translate spanish Day2_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_f43be276:

    # n side sad_closed "It really does. I thought Satoshi was one of a kind." with dissolve
    n side sad_closed "Vaya que sí. Pensé que Satoshi era el único en su tipo." with dissolve

